These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, tower, ranch-style
4 different games are played: monopoly, go, billiard, whist
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the person playing go is the ranch-style house##1
2. the person playing billiard is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person playing go is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| House   | cape-cod    | ranch-style    | gothic-revival      | tower    |
| Game   | whist | go | billiard | monopoly |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

