.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, coffee, fanta
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bike, motorbike, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person drinking coffee and the person driving the roller##2
6. the person driving the bus is between the person watching western movies and the person drinking fanta##2
7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Beverage           | fanta      | coffee       | 7up      | milk       |
| Transport         | bike    | bus | motorbike | roller |

