.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
City: hamburg, miami, rome, berlin
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, lemonade, water
1. the paramedic is the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person traveling to rome and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City        | miami | rome     | hamburg   | berlin     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | milk | 7up  | water    |

