The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, october, june, march
 1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person who growsiris is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Flower          | orchid         | iris         | dahlia     | balloon-flower      |
