3. the polish is between the person traveling to marseilles and the dutch##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
9. the person who growslily is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Flower   | lily      | iris       | rose     | amaryllis      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| City         | berlin   | rome    | edinburgh | marseilles   |

