The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, analyst, architect, dancer
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person who growsdahlia is the architect##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the architect and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1
 5. the dancer is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the social-worker is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
10. the architect is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | tulip | dahlia | begonia  | amaryllis  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Job   | social-worker   | architect   | dancer | analyst |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

