The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, gardening, drawing, cooking
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, quad-bike, subway
1. the fan of electronic is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the car##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the fan of r&b##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of funk##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water   | iced-tea    | juice  |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | electronic   | r&b | ambient |
| Hobby           | woodworking       | drawing   | gardening        | cooking  |
| Transport     | quad-bike | jet-ski | car         | subway |

