 3. the fisherman is the malaysian##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the designer is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the accountant is between the social-worker and the dutch##2
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
