.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
City: boston, hamburg, new-york, berlin
There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, daffodil, rose
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| City   | hamburg    | new-york    | berlin      | boston |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Flower      | daffodil | daisy | rose | iris        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

