The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, action, epic, western
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, train, van
 1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the person eating kale is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person who likes green is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
 5. the person who likes green is between the person who likes turquise and the person who likes pink##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes pink is the person driving the train##1
10. the person watching musical movies is the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food        | cherry  | cucumber | kale     | carrot     |
| Color         | pink | green | turquise     | blood-red |
| Movie-Genre       | action  | western   | musical | epic    |
| Transport   | train   | subway   | jet-ski  | van        |

